  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a wok or large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add curry paste and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add lemongrass and galangal and cook for 2 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add mushrooms and cook for 3 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Pour in coconut milk and coconut water, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to medium-low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Add fish sauce, lime juice, and brown sugar, and stir to combine.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Stir in chopped cilantro and serve hot."
